17
00:01:24,219 --> 00:01:28,319
ask you if you're sure with a cigarette sticking
out of their box directly in your face and

18
00:01:28,319 --> 00:01:32,750
of course, you give in, because you haven't
replaced any of these steps. You just stopped

19
00:01:32,750 --> 00:01:37,799
consuming the reward, you stopped the routine
by not smoking, but you still do feel the

20
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:41,429
urge and a cigarette is still what would satisfy
that need.

21
00:01:41,430 --> 00:01:46,200
